title: China looms large over Biden’s trip to Vietnam
description: President Joe Biden’s visit to Vietnam this weekend may be short, but it has major implications for American efforts to push back against China.

title: Tourists describe moments earthquake struck Morocco: 'We don't know what to do next'
description: Tourists visiting Marrakech, Morocco describe the moment a 6.8-magnitude earthquake struck the country, the aftershocks and the damage left behind.

title: Video show the moment 6.8-magnitude earthquake strikes Morocco
description: Surveillance footage captured the moments a 6.8-magnitude earthquake struck Morocco in the city of Marrakech.

title: Drone video shows earthquake devastation in south Morocco
description: Drone video captures the damage of a 6.8. magnitude earthquake that struck Morocco, killing at least a thousand people. Search and rescue missions have begun in the southern city of Taroudant.

title: Footage shows buildings in ruins after Morocco earthquake
description: Videos show buildings reduced to rubble after a 6.8-magnitude earthquake struck Morocco near the city of Marrakech. The Moroccan army has been mobilized for search and rescue teams to find and rescue any survivors.

title: G20 adds the African Union as a member, issues call rejecting use of force in reference to Ukraine
description: NEW DELHI, India — The Group of 20 top world economies welcomed the African Union as a member at their annual summit Saturday, but their wording on the contentious issue of Russia’s war in Ukraine was limited to a call to avoid forcefully seizing territory or using nuclear weapons.

title: U.K. police catch terrorism suspect who escaped from a London prison
description: A former soldier who escaped from a London prison while awaiting trial on terrorism charges was captured Saturday, police said.

title: Hundreds dead after 6.8-magnitude earthquake strikes Morocco
description: Video captured the aftermath of a 6.8-magnitude earthquake in Morocco that killed hundreds of people. The powerful quake toppled buildings and sent people fleeing from their homes.

title: Record rainfall slams Hong Kong, leaving over 100 injured
description: Historic rainfall has paralyzed Hong Kong, washing out roads and flooding buildings. The deadly storm is the heaviest in over a century, leaving over 100 people injured.
